      "text": "Arquivo de manifesto <package.json> --> Especificações\n    - Utilizar-se-á npm (node package mananger)\n    - `npm init`\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Arquivo de manifesto <package.json> --> Especificações\n    - Utilizar-se-á npm (node package mananger)\n    - `npm init`\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "V3EqtjF_VY53WSnbnO-WN",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 94,
      "y": 786.1875,
      "width": 755.3795166015625,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
